												<p>These &#8221; Chocolate Chipotle Brownies&#8221; ,are screaming,&#8221;Take only with a gallon of cold milk,and if desires still remain,bake another batch &#8221; !!! I have learned many wonderful things,from you &#8220;Ladies&#8221;,and my cooking has improved &#8220;Very Much&#8221;,over the year!! My two little granddaughters,come in from school,and look on the bar,if I played it easy,and made sandwiches today,the 5 year old looks and says&#8221;is this all you done,I want some scratch food and cakes&#8221;!! My daughter and all the rest,say &#8220;I have spoiled them,that no one can get by with sandwiches,or cheap food joints,they are very verbal,about taste!!! Oh Well,I think I&#8217;m the winner here!! Thanks,Jim</p>
